<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1057] Trim whitespaces from user specified configs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1057</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Whitespaces in configs are a common problem that leads to config errors. It will be nice if Kafka can trim the whitespaces from configs automatically&lt;/p&gt;</description>
